high_descs: go to the dining table
pick up the knife from the table
take the knife to the counter with the toaster
cut the loaf on the counter
take the knife to the fridge
put the knife in the fridge
go back to the counter with the toaster
pick up a slice of bread from the loaf
take the slice to the fridge
put it in then take back out
take the chilled bread slice to the microwave
put the slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: cut a slice of bread, chill it, then cook it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the table with cabbage and a knife
Pick the knife from the table
Turn around and go to the counter with a toaster
Cut the fruit  to the right of the toaster
Take the knife and go to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the knife on the tray on the top
Go back to the cut fruit
Pick a slice of the fruit
Carry the slice and go to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the slice on the tray below that with the knife, wait a few seconds, and take the slice out of the fridge
Take the slice and go to the cabinet with a microwave on its top
Put the slice inside the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled slice of the fruit inside the microwave

high_descs: Turn right and head to the left side of the round table
Pick up the knife on the round table
Turn right then walk straight turn left face the bread on the counter
Slice the bread
Turn left then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the knife then close it
Turn left then go back to the counter that has bread
Pick up a slice of bread
Turn back to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the bread
Turn right then head to the microwave on your right
Open the microwave put in the sliced bread then close it
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled sliced bread to the microwave
